\u00e5 hvordan det arter seg i politiske resultater s\u00e5 er det ikke noe entydig bilde, sier han."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "kultur"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "32c0b8b163237311f715b652f4eeec69031919300f8b868484edaf6c0d66fe87"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-05-01T01:46:10.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Hans Rotmo med nytt utfall mot muslimske innvandrere."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/kultur/article11141653.ece/sa71ch/ALTERNATES/w980-default/IMG_nhtRotmo1.jpg_2_1_1946221.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/f47e91f024197c0e430eac882d6553c954e28c54.jpg?59821cd6"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["- Muslimene er en milj\u00f8forurensning i Europa -adressa.no", "- Kryr som lopp og lus", "- Muslimske ghettoer", "- Ikke overraskende"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "f47e91f024197c0e430eac882d6553c954e28c54"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["Hans Rotmo", "V\u00f8mm\u00f8lfestivalen"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "Hans Rotmo,V\u00f8mm\u00f8lfestivalen"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": "kultur"}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "religion-and-spirituality"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["radikale venstresiden", "muslimsk", "muslimsk innvandring", "muslimske ghettoer"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["hans rotmo", "geert wilders", "tr\u00f8nder-avisa", "asyls\u00f8keran", "indianer", "v\u00f8mm\u00f8lfestivalen", "antirasistisk senter", "adresseavisen", "trossetrua", "svarte", "eurotrua"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["danmark", "europa", "oslo", "verdal"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["rune berglund steen", "\u00f8yvind str\u00f8mmen", "lars hedegaard"]}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": "kultur"}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "ht